staticWebApps.description: An Azure Static Web Apps (Preview) extension for Visual Studio Code.
staticWebApps.enableOutputTimestamps: Prepends each line displayed in the output channel with a timestamp.
staticWebApps.deleteConfirmation: The behavior to use when confirming delete of a resource group.
staticWebApps.deleteConfirmation.EnterNa: Prompts with an input box where you enter the resource group name to delete.
staticWebApps.deleteConfirmation.ClickBu: Prompts with a warning dialog where you click a button to delete.
